Self Organising Learning Environment

Welcome to the Innersummit's Self Organising Learning Zone (SOLE). Here you will find all the resources that you need for your course. If you are visiting for the first time you will be able to have a tour of our demonstration resources so that you get a feel of exactly what we provide when you enrol on one of our accredited or training programmes.

item.description:
The Name Innersummit? | Innersummit Ltd

Innersummit is all about those moments in business life that you have to dig a bit deeper in order to keep on moving forwards. It is the time when you need to continue believing that you can make it through a situation, which is over whelming.
